WEBVTT

00:01.293 --> 00:02.325
[DOORBELL RINGS]

00:04.129 --> 00:06.253
There's your <i>Other Realm Gazette.</i>
I need to collect.

00:06.423 --> 00:07.622
You're the newspaper boy?

00:07.799 --> 00:11.798
My mother took a lot of folic acid
when I was in utero.

00:12.012 --> 00:13.424
My aunts aren't home,
I don't have money.

00:13.639 --> 00:15.015
Little Mikey gets stiffed.

00:15.557 --> 00:18.263
- Can you come back tomorrow?
- Oh, sure, come back tomorrow.

00:18.435 --> 00:21.188
"Oh, I don't get paid till Friday."
Everybody's got an excuse.

00:21.355 --> 00:23.763
- I give excellent service, but--
- Excellent service?

00:23.982 --> 00:26.023
Last Tuesday's paper
was from 1948,

00:26.193 --> 00:28.317
and Monday's paper
was wrapped around a fish.

00:28.529 --> 00:29.940
I've been sick.

00:30.155 --> 00:32.279
When we get our replacement papers,
you'll get paid.

00:32.491 --> 00:34.319
Fine.

00:34.868 --> 00:35.900
[DOORBELL RINGS]

00:36.078 --> 00:38.237
[THUNDER CRASHES]

00:41.834 --> 00:45.120
Oh, well, it looks like
it's gonna be sunny tomorrow.

